posting_body: ['OPEN VIEWS / HIGH CEILINGS / GYM / CONCIERGE / THREE OUTDOOR SPACES / WASHER & DRYER / PARKING', 'Listing ID #: 212642', 'Price: $4,850', 'Property Type: Apartment', 'Bedrooms: 1.0', 'Bathrooms: 1.0', 'Approx.', 'Size: 695 Sq.', 'Ft.', 'Building Amenities', 'Bicycle Room', 'Doorman', 'Elevator', 'Lounge', 'Roof Deck', 'An amazing opportunity in the incredible neighborhood of Tribeca.', 'This fantastic unit has been finished with high quality materials and offers you maximum convenience.', 'Take advantage of the generous amenities and THREE OUTDOOR SPACES unique to the building along with a generous array of amenities.', 'This beautiful and recently constructed (2001) luxury apartment building pleasantly overlooks Foley Square.', 'It is also conveniently located within walking distance of many of Downtown Manhattan’s other attractions including Soho, Greenwich Village, the Financial District, Chinatown, and Little Italy.', 'The building offers many premier recreation and relaxation facilities.', "Tribeca is a phenomenal neighborhood featuring upscale restaurants and boutiques that make up it's chic commercial center, while quiet cobblestone streets and impressive loft buildings lend the area an air of tranquility.", 'For showings contact: Adel Talebpour / Bouklis Group / 212-961-7334 (Cell) / <URL> / <URL> / <URL>', 'Adel Talebpour', 'Phone: 212-402-7855', 'Mobile: 212-961-7334', 'Email: <URL>', 'The Bouklis Group \xa0 212-402-7855 \xa0 212-961-7334 \xa0 <URL>', 'POSTED BY REALTYMX™', 'To view, call or text Adel Talebpour at 212-961-7334']
